name: GENESIS - The Scream after Edvard Munch

metadata.name: Women08
metadata.description:
Women08 - 1/1 piece, acrylic and oils pastel on canvas - Work is digitalised.
A very close piece to my heart & serve as my identity at web3 space.

This is my genesis collection of 4/4 and first ever work minted on the blockchain, kickstarting my web3 / NFT journey.

Every piece in this collection is a representation of the inner challenges a woman goes through in her life to balance her personal, family, career, and spiritual life. She often swallows her screams as a sign of survival.

Dedicating this collection to every woman in Web3.
